high_descs: Turn around and walk to the stove on your right.
Pick up a pan from the stove.
Walk to the counter on your left.
Place the pan on the counter.
Return to the stove.
Pick up a pan from the stove.
Return to the counter on your left.
Place the pan on the counter.
anns.task_desc: Place two pans on a counter.

high_descs: turn left and walk over to the stove in the kitchen
grab the sauce pan off of the front right burner
move left a bit to face the other kitchen top counter
place the sauce pan down in front of the lettuce
back up a bit to face the stove again
grab the second sauce pan off of the stove
move to the left again and face that same counter
place the sauce pan down on the counter to the right of the apple
anns.task_desc: put both pans from the burner on to the kitchen counter top

high_descs: Turn right, walk towards the fridge and then turn left and go to the stove.
Pick up the nearest pan on the stove top.
Turn left and walk to the counter top.
Put the pan down to the left of the white bottle.
Turn back around and go back to the stove.
Pick up the other pan on the stove top.
Turn left and walk to the counter top.
Put the pan down to the right of the apple.
anns.task_desc: Move both pans from the stove top to the white counter top.
